Category	     Command      	Action	          Description
Modes	           
                M	            Manual Mode	      Aap car ko khud control karenge.
                A	            Auto Mode	        Car obstacle avoid karke khud chalegi.
                X	            Line Follower  	  Car black line ko follow karegi.
                P	            Smart Parking	    Car slot scan karke reverse park hogi.
Movement	
                F	            Forward	          Car aage jayegi (Safety active).
                B	            Backward	        Car piche jayegi (Safety active).
                L	            Left	            Car left muregi.
                R	            Right	            Car right muregi.
                S	            Stop	            Car ruk jayegi + Brake Lights ON.
Lights	
                H1	          Headlight ON	    Front white LEDs jal jayengi.
                H2          	Headlight OFF	    Front white LEDs band ho jayengi.
Sound	
                h1	          Horn ON	          Buzzer bajna shuru hoga.
                hh2           Horn OFF       	  Buzzer band ho jayega.
